\CE[94]\OC[30]\N<Phils>Um... I started feeling a sense of discomfort

It's like, there's this uncomfortable atmosphere

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[30]\N<Phils>Yes! That's exactly it. At first, it seemed like I

'Head towards the dungeon northeast of the city gate'
